All content of the Dow Jones branded indices © S&P Dow Jones Indices LLC 2015 and/or its affiliates., 4070=The GreenHaven Continuous Commodity Index Fund (GCC) is an Exchange-Traded Product (ETP) that provides an innovative and efficient way to deliver broad based, diversified commodity exposure. It aims to achieve this by using futures contracts to track the Continuous Commodity Index-Total Return (CCI-TR).
